Posts.Content: I have recently found a lump in my breast. I am really freaked out and have been for a while now. I recently have been been doing some of my own research due to getting two different diagnoses from two different doctors. I have cancer, I don't have cancer????? I came accross this and now after seeing this on YouTube I've really lost faith in our healthcare system: www.youtube.com/watch?v=aqNjdrdVll0 Where will it all end?
Posts.Title: AFRAID TO SEE A DOCTOR!!!!
